file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: RTD Token Manager API
  description: ''
  version: v3
servers:
  - url: https://${host}/rtd/token/
paths:
  /bin-ranges/links:
    get:
      summary: Get Temporary link to download bin range details
      operationId: getBinRangeLink
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/LinksResponse'
        '404':
          description: Not Found
        '500':
          description: Internal Server Error
  /token-list/public-key:
    get:
      summary: Get public PGP key for acquirer files
      operationId: getTokenListPublicPGPKey
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
        '401':
          description: Access Denied
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
        '404':
          description: Not Found
        '500':
          description: Internal Server Error
  /token-list:
    post:
      summary: Upload acquirer file
      operationId: uploadAcquirerTokenFile
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/TokenListUploadRequest'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/TokenListUploadResponse'
        '401':
          description: Access Denied
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
        '404':
          description: Not Found
        '500':
          description: Internal Server Error
  /known-hashes/links:
    get:
      summary: Get temporary links to download known hpans and htokens
      operationId: getKnownHashes
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/LinksResponse'
        '401':
          description: Access Denied
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
        '404':
          description: Not Found
        '500':
          description: Internal Server Error
components:
  schemas:
    LinksResponse:
      required:
        - fileLinks
      type: object
      properties:
        fileLinks:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          description: List of links needed to download file
        numberOfFiles:
          type: integer
        availableUntil:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          pattern: "dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss"
        generationDate:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          pattern: "dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss"
    TokenListUploadRequest:
      required:
        - file
      type: object
      properties:
        file:
          type: string
          format: binary
          description: File to upload
    TokenListUploadResponse:
      required:
        - filename
      type: object
      properties:
        filename:
          type: string
          description: Filename of the uploaded file
    Error:
      required:
        - statusCode
        - message
      type: object
      properties:
        statusCode:
          type: integer
          description: The code identifies the error
          example: 401
        message:
          type: string
          description: Error description
          example: Access denied due to missing subscription key
    Salt:
      type: string
  securitySchemes:
    apiKeyHeader:
      type: apiKey
      name: Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key
      in: header
    apiKeyQuery:
      type: apiKey
      name: subscription-key
      in: query
security:
  - apiKeyHeader: [ ]
  - apiKeyQuery: [ ]
